  "text": "As explained in Section 2, alternative NGA providers target a geographically delimited group of customers and differentiate their offer in terms of either coverage or speed. In fact, they address a niche market resulting from both market and policy failures [CITATION_1] , as private and public players were unable to fully satisfy the demand for faster connectivity.",
